          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2450538-louise?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2450538-louise?shelf=food">food</a>
