<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/798875.Alone_in_the_Kitchen_with_an_Eggplant_"><img alt="Alone in the Kitchen with an Eggplant : Confessions of Cooking for One and Dining Alone" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1442732703l/798875._SX98_.jpg" />
